title: [Misoka Nagatsuki] A Day in the Life {Loliconnection, Zero Degre
description:
Today, I'm posting a translated manga that was originally a project of the
now defunct... I think they're defunct... Loliconnection.

For the longest, the translation of this manga has been left incomplete
much to the dismay of many fans. I manage to recently dig up the RAW
files, so I took it upon myself to revive the project and complete the last
two chapters. (Besides, I was just as curious and anticipant to see the
story conclude.)

Without further ado, I present to you "A Day In The Life" by the Beat-...
err.. I mean, by Misoka Nagatsuki. ^_^;;

Bear with me my connection is slow and iffy today.
